    "title": "Lead SEO Specialist at Rivigo South Asia Partners",
    "description": "Join the Rivigo South Asia Partners family as a SEO Specialist in Howrah. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Rivigo South Asia Partners:\nRivigo South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Howrah, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Rivigo South Asia Partners!",
